{"tid":1607071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無論你無勇武定和班非都好 聽日都記得包好自己","createTime":"2019-09-30T17:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T01:29:51.000Z","uid":95646,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fa203347b8e6eb4309c735f5816de1acb95d7429","tid":1607071,"uid":95646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:24:04.000Z","msg":"雖然講黎都係老生長談 但希望都唔嫌長氣俾小弟講多次<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1.記得一定要BLACKBLOC 所有野全黑</span></span> <br />\n盡量包好自己 戴帽戴口罩<br />\n一定要帶多件衫換 而家啲狗亂咬人<br />\n上車前就好換衫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2. 背囊記得用RAIN COVER</span></span> <br />\n遮LOGO之餘俾狗撲都可以金蟬脫殼<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">3. 腰包就係必須 袋好自己證件</span></span> <br />\n唔好擺係背囊 如果唔係金蟬脫殼都冇用<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">4. 面巾入面最好戴返多個口罩</span></span><br />\n有啲手足啲面巾太薄太緊都清楚突顯到啲五官<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5. 記得交低身份證俾屋企人/身邊相熟朋友先</span></span><br />\n聽日有咩時間第一時間搵星火都好<br />\n自己都要背熟星火電話 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">98190979</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">6. 唔好搭黨鐵 唔好用八達通</span></span><br />\n黨鐵從來都唔安全<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">7. 和理非幫幫手分工帶夠物資support勇武</span></span><br />\n唔好兩手FING FING 唔好當去嘉年華<br />\n做個真正SUPPORT到前線嘅和理非<br />\n<br />\n各位未買齊野嘅盡量試下聽朝買齊<br />\n唔好諗住靠到時現場有人有多<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n祝大家聽日武運昌隆 <br />\n一定要打狗救人"},{"pid":"f9faa020cf45a5c6da828181afa62916911c0719","tid":1607071,"uid":95646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:25:03.000Z","msg":"標題打錯 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和<span style=\"color: red;\">理</span>非</span>"},{"pid":"53e80785f6eabf4a3b2f30b14033a76d4e1fa624","tid":1607071,"uid":95646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:29:31.000Z","msg":"賀佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aa0c731f5736b4536be6d05af12fcb2beb2662b","tid":1607071,"uid":95646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:30:16.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3c02e6a86319d75615b6b7b1a4c7f7241dd6eb","tid":1607071,"uid":95646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Um7VCrz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUm7VCrz.jpg&h=d93bb94c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ueVPGTf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FueVPGTf.jpg&h=c60a87ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616742be4f831d3819b5beefd69fbaf28b5bfc80","tid":1607071,"uid":95646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:33:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc8c7335458345e811ae5641b452de20b1dfaa2","tid":1607071,"uid":95646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:36:54.000Z","msg":"記得用腰包呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad082d09dc4fc3e3574f752d90388bfda1cbada","tid":1607071,"uid":211270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:40:33.000Z","msg":"國殤日剪回鄉證<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1606996\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1606996</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9182f65d5d236d27f4f5ba6eb